instruction: Generate a rap about your favorite basketball team.
output:
Yeah, it's all about the Los Angeles Lakers,
Dodging their opponents like they know they don't need favors.
Kobe and Shaq running the show,
Winning championships making everybody go - Woah!
Champs in the paint, always on defense,
The Lakers have been playing with such excellence.
LeBron and AD starting up the heat,
Nothing else to say - this squad can't be beat!
From the Staples Center to the other side of town,
The Lakers flyin' high and it's never going down.
Champs over and over with every dunk,
That's why the Lakers reign - call it their royal junk!
